description: Mai Thai Wings, Shrimp Banh Mi, Dry Hu Tieu, and so much more! 3 Brothers Kitchen brings Asian Fusion to a new level on the streets of San Jose. Utilizing the flavors of the Filipino, Hawaiian, Thai, Vietnamese, and other cultures, 3 Brothers' unique spin on classic dishes will leave you wanting more! Find them roaming the streets of San Jose, or at an event around the Bay Area!
name: 3 Brothers Kitchen
